Cell["\<\
The OpenQASM 3 of a circuit, serialized exactly as built: Transpile the same \
circuit to a native gate set: Route onto a device coupling map, emitting \
two-qubit gates in the calibrated direction:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"cb26c953-e03c-4850-bc62-26139ad13126"],

