Cell["\<\
Take an algorithm built in the framework and emit native, routed OpenQASM 3 \
ready for a hardware compiler \[LongDash] decomposed to the device gate set \
and mapped onto its connectivity:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"9ae015c9-a181-4f2f-886e-7339f5467c56"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

